window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The heart-pounding conclusion to the best-selling InterWorld series from Neil Gaiman, Michael Reaves, and Mallory Reaves! <i>Eternity's Wheel</i> is full of time and space travel, magic, science, and the bravery of a young boy who must now face his destiny as a young man. </p> <p>Joey Harker never wanted to be a leader. But he's the one everyone is looking to now that FrostNight looms, and he'll have to step up if he has any hope of saving InterWorld, the Multiverse, and everything in between. </p>"; 
